[{"id":"14a3488414402a9208063e2a192627ef","from":"isee systems","from_email":"info@iseesystems.com","to":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to_list":[{"name":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"Announcing 2008 isee User Conference","date":"2007-12-20T15:10:08.000Z","formatted_date":"Dec 20, 2007","formatted_time":"3:10 PM","body":"2008 isee User Conference\nMaking Connections\n\nIt\u2019s on our calendar and we\u2019d love for you to put it on yours!\n\nDates:\nOctober 9-10, 2008\n\nPlace:\nBurlington Sheraton,\nBurlington, Vermont\n\nWho:\niThink and STELLA Enthusiasts\n\nAbout the Conference\n\nThis is a great opportunity for iThink and STELLA users from business,\neducation, research and consulting to:\n\n    * share Systems Thinking experience,\n    * learn new skills and tricks,\n    * meet experts in the field,\n    * try out new ideas for models and simulations, and\n    * get a sneak peek into the future of isee systems \n      products and training.\n\nThe two days will be filled with keynote addresses by Systems Thinking\nleaders, iThink and STELLA application stories and case studies,\nfield-specific round tables, poster sessions, and time for networking and\nopen discussion.\n\nAfter the conference, enjoy Vermont\u2019s fall foliage and the gorgeous Lake\nChamplain region. The Sheraton will extend your conference rates through\nthe weekend.\n\nTo learn more about the conference or to find out how you can participate,\nvisit www.iseesystems.com/userconference\n\n\n**********************************************************\nwww.iseesystems.com\nPhone: (603) 448-4990 | Fax: (603) 448-4992\n\nTo unsubscribe from the isee mailing list, please visit this link:\nhttp://www.iseesystems.com/aspx/remove.aspx?email=jeeproject@yahoo.com\n\n","body_html":"<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN\">\n<HTML>\n<HEAD>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=Windows-1252\">\n\n</HEAD>\n<BODY lan